# Locally downloaded font assets (Noto Sans KR etc.) — too large for git.
# Samples reference fonts/ via paths the user provides locally. The leading
# slash anchors the rule to the repo root so docs/demo/fonts/ (committed,
# subsetted redistributables) is not affected.
/fonts/
